Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得·艾伦·泰勒是我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Peter Alan Tyler, my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他是世界上最棒的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The most wonderful man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,生于1954年9月15日\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Born 15th September, 1954.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 洛斯 过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come here, Rose. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁呀 -这是你爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who's that? - It's your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他去世的时候你还太小 应该不记得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You weren't old enough to remember when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,1987年11月7日\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}1987, 7th November.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得我是怎么告诉你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you remember what I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就在斯图尔特·霍斯金斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The day that Stuart Hoskins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和萨拉·克拉克结婚那一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and Sarah Clark got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他总是喜欢去冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He was always having adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他要是能看到现在的你一定会很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He would have loved to have seen you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.79,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈经常会这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's what Mum always says.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在想 我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So I was thinking, could we...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能不能回到我爸爸还活着的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}could we go and see my dad when he was still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是心血来潮吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where's this come from all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果不行的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All right, if we can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这违反了什么时空规则\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}if it goes against the laws of time or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那就算了 不用管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}then never mind, just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我什么都能做 我只是更担心你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, I can do anything. I'm just more worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谨遵所命 但你要小心你所许的愿望\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your wish is my command. But be careful what you wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn黑体\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\pos(189.538,186.4)\c&HFFFFFF&}{\fsp3\fs38\t(\fsp3\fs42}神秘博士{\fsp1\fs18\t(\fs20\fsp1}第一季第八集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(600,600)\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\pos(189.538,171.6)}父亲节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我 彼得·艾伦·泰勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I, Peter Alan Tyler,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意娶杰奎琳·安德列·苏泽特·普兰提斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}take you, Jacqueline Andrea Suzette Prentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我 彼得·艾伦·泰勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I, Peter Alan Tyler,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意娶杰奎琳…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}take you, Jacqueline...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泽…苏西…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Susanne, Suzette...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Anita?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧 没叫我狄姑娘已经很不错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just carry on. It's good enough for Lady Di.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为他会更高点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I thought he'd be taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,作为我的合法妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}To be my lawful wedded wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,相亲相爱相互扶持 唯有死亡能将我们分开\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}To love and behold till death us do part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他死在我们家附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He died so close to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时不在场 没人在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wasn't there. Nobody was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一起肇事逃逸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was a hit-and-run driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一直没找到肇事者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Never found out who.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,救护车到的时候他已经咽气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He was dead when the ambulance got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望当时有人能陪着他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I only wish there'd been someone there for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想陪着他 他就不用孤独地死去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I want to be that someone. So he doesn't die alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,11月7日吗 -1987年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}November 7th? - 1987.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太诡异了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我父亲死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The day my father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为一整天都会阴沉沉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I thought it'd be all sort of grim and stormy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实不过是普通的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's just an ordinary day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,过去这里是另一个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The past is another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,1987年这里就是怀特岛郡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}1987 is just the Isle of Wight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定要去吗 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You sure about this? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里 乔丹路\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is it. Jordan Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他迟到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他是去拿结婚礼物的 一个花瓶\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He'd been to get a wedding present, a vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈经常说 "那该死的花瓶"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mum always said, "That stupid vase".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他下了车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He got out of his car...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后过马路\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and crossed the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 就是这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, God, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看他 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Go to him. Quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在太晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,救护车来之前 他就死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}By the time the ambulance got there, he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能就这样一个人死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He can't die on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我能再试试吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can I try again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是之前的我和你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right, that's the first you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个坏主意 同时出现了两对我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's a very bad idea, two sets of us being here at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点 别让他们看到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just be careful they don't see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等到她跑开然后他跟过去时 去找你爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Wait till she runs off and he follows then go to your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 就是这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, God, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想的话不必强求\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't have to do anything you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是我们最后一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But this is the last time we can be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我做到了 我救了你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did it. I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 他开得多快 你记下车牌号了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Blimey, did you see the speed of it? Did you get his number?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的成功了 天呐 你还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I really did it. Oh, my God, look at you, you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那辆车差点撞死你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That car was gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 我看到他开过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Give me some credit, I did see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我又没打算撞过去 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wasn't gonna walk under it, was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真巧 我女儿也叫这个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's a coincidence. That's my daughter's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个好名字 这个选择不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's a great name. Good choice. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我得快点了 还得去参加婚礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right. I better shift. I've got a wedding to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是萨拉·克拉克的婚礼吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is that Sarah Clark's wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你也去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah. Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要我搭你和你男朋友一程吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you and your boyfriend need a lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧 不好意思这么乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right, there we go, sorry about the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想喝茶的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If you want a cup of tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,厨房在那边 牛奶在冰箱里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}kitchen's down there, milk's in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不过牛奶除了放冰箱里还能放哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It would be, wouldn't it? Where else would you put the milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢 还是可以放在窗台上的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mind you, there's always the windowsill outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I always thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人发明了一种特殊的窗台牛奶箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}if someone invented a windowsill with special compartments,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一边放牛奶 一边放酸奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}one for milk, one for yoghurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,准能赚好多钱 专门卖给学生之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}make a lot of money out of that. Sell it to students and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该记下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I should write that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别介意 不好意思 我得去换个衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Anyway, never mind that. Excuse me, I got to go and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是他的东西 妈妈都收起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All the stuff mum kept. His stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她把这些东西都打包塞到碗橱里去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She kept it all packed away in boxes in the cupboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她喝了点酒就会拿出来给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She used to show me when she'd had a bit to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都摆在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Here it is, on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,摆在原来的位置上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,保龄球第三名 第两名可以去迪德科特\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Third prize at the bowling. First two got to go to Didcot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,养生饮料\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Health drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈经常说是开胃水\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Tonics Mum used to call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他就靠卖这些花草饮料赚钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He made his money selling this Vitex stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他干过各种活 他很聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He had all sorts of jobs, he was so clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳能 妈妈说他本来是准备做这个的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Solar power. Mum said he was going to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他能如愿以偿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我会告诉他你不是我男朋友的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Okay, I'll tell him you're not my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们见面时我说"和我一起在宇宙中旅行吧"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}When we met I said, "Travel with me in space".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你拒绝了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You said, "No".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我说"时光机器"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then I said, "time machine".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是什么策划已久的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It wasn't some big plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是看着这一切然后想"我能阻止"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I just saw it happening, and I thought, "I can stop it".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我又这样 又挑了个愚蠢的原始人旅伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did it again. I picked another stupid ape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不是想畅游宇宙 根本不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not about showing you the universe. It never is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你是为了利用宇宙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's about the universe doing something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只准你自己穿越时空\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So it's okay when you go to other times
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,去拯救别人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and you save people's lives
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我救我父亲就不行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but not when it's me saving my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我在干什么 你不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know what I'm doing, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,两对我们同时出现会让那段空间变得很不稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Two sets of us being there made that a vulnerable point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但他还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的星球毁灭了 还有我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My entire planet died, my whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我从没想过回到过去拯救他们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you think it never occurred to me to go back and save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但我又没改变什么历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's not like I've changed history.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说没改变多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not much. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他又不会成为什么世界领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}he's never gonna be a world leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他也不会挑起第三次世界大战\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}he's not gonna start World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 有个原本应该死去的人现在还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose, there's a man alive in the world who wasn't alive before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,普通人 正是这个自然界中最重要的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}An ordinary man. That's the most important thing in creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,整个世界都会因为他而发生改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The whole world's different because he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你更希望他死吗 -我不是说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Would you rather him dead? - I'm not saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你不是我生命中最重要的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}For once, you're not the most important man in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们看看没了我之后你怎么办 把钥匙给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let's see how you get on without me. Give me the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,塔迪斯的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The TARDIS key.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我这么不重要 还给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If I'm so insignificant, give it me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 还给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All right then, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在得到你想要的结果了 再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've got what you wanted so that's goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你吓不到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很难过 你过一会就会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know how sad you are. You'll be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你会在塔迪斯外面晃悠等着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Or you'll hang around outside the TARDIS waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你等很久很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And I'll make you wait a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跟男朋友吵架了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Boyfriend trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你在整理什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me, do you mind? What are you tidying up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 习惯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sorry, force of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别为他烦心 小两口就是会吵架的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't worry about him. Couples have rows all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是一对 为什么大家都觉我们是一对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We're not a couple. Why does everyone think we're a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他离开我了 -你这么靓的妹子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think he left me. - What? A pretty girl like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,换我肯定会… -打住\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was going out with you... - Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm just saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你要说什么 还是别往那方面想吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know what you're saying and we're not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们根本不能往那方面想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}At no point are we going anywhere near there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道那方面是哪方面…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You aren't even aware that there exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想去想那方面的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't want to think about there and,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 你也不想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}believe me, neither do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那方面对你来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There, for you, is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟百慕大三角一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}like the Bermuda Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 你可真会哄人开心 -我们走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Blimey, you know how to flatter a bloke. - Right. Are we off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你这就不会让人误会了吗 -当然不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That wouldn't be a mixed signal at all? - Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是把你送回疯人院去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll take you back to the loony bin where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我相信好像在哪见过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Except I'm sure I've met you somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's weird. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好多人都不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's so many people missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬叔叔 琳恩阿姨 巴克斯特家的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Uncle Steven, Auntie Lynn, all the Baxters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得有点不对劲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't think something's gone wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这是天赐的良机让你能好好考虑考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe it's a godsend, gives you time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用完成婚礼的 这年头不在乎这个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't have to go through with it, not these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔也放纵一下嘛 -爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Live in sin for a bit. - Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,十年之内你就会说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}In 10 years' time, you'll turn round and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"要是能让时光倒流就好了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}"If only I could turn the clock back."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的问题还是真的变冷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is it me or did it just get cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在赛马场碰到这家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I met this bloke at the horses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他分了我点版税\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and he's cutting me in on copyright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我以为你是个正经的生意人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But I thought you were a proper businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想啊 我什么都干一点 养家糊口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wish. I do a bit of this, bit of that. I scrape by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 肯定是我听错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right. I must've heard wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以其实你有点打肿脸充胖子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So, really, you're a bit of a Del Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Shoot me down in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会碰巧认识我太太吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're not related to my wife by any chance, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 她也会去婚礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God. She's gonna be at the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪 你认识她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie? Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那她跟你谈过我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's she told you about me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她嫁给了世上最棒的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She said she'd picked the most fantastic man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那肯定是另一个杰琪 她从没这么说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Must be a different Jackie, then. She'd never say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这种音乐听得我头疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This stuff goes right over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这歌应该还没出呢吧 -没出就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's not out yet. - Good job and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我得看看短信 -什么叫短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm just gonna check my messages. - How do you mean? Messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是电话吗 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is that a phone? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,华生 过来 我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Watson, come here. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,华生 过来 我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Watson, come here. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,华生 过来 我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Watson, come here. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,半数客人没出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Half the guests haven't turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好别过来 简直是一场灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're better off not being here, it's a disaster in the making.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我看这就是"未婚先孕"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, in this case, "Knocked her up" is a phrase I'd use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,华生 过来 我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Watson, come here. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hello? Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,华生 过来 我需要…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Watson, come here. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快进来 不能在婚礼前看到新娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Dad, get inside. We can't see the bride before the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,会带来厄运的 -你遇到她就是厄运\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's bad luck. - Bad luck when you met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 今天是被诅咒的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I tell you, this day is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这才叫蛋糕裙嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now that's what I call a meringue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,斯图尔特的爸爸都打算走人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stuart's dad said go round the block
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为人们都不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}'Cause there's people missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How do you mean, missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫没来 苏尼塔没来 比尔没来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's no Dave, no Sunita, no Bee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,羊旗俱乐部的人也没来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's no one from The Lamb and Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的拖尾又裂开了 我就应该用魔术贴的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My train's detached again. I knew I should have used Velcro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有我呢 别发牢骚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm here, stop your bellyaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我照顾一下洛斯好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Take Rose a sec, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她可真漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ain't she pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个小淑女 这才像话嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's a little madam, that's what she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要人来帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I need more hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她那个没用的爸爸到哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where's her useless article of a dad got to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那辆车 就是之前那辆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's that car. Same one as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就在眼前的 跑哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was right in front of us, where's he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我爸爸 你为什么这么叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You called me "Dad"? What did you say that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 他来了 等着他又闯祸吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, wonderful! Here he is, the accident waiting to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就你这样估计连自己的葬礼都会迟到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You'd be late for your own funeral and it nearly was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,又没误事 -这是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No damage done. - And who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你张着嘴巴看什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What are you looking at with your mouth open?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你的头发 -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your hair. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've never seen it like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮 你的头发很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it's lovely, your hair's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你抱着的宝宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And that baby you're holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的宝宝吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That would be your baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,又是你的某个马子吗 -她救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Another one of yours, is she? - She saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个理由挺新鲜的啊 上次是什么来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's a new one. What was it last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不认识她 她就是个衣帽间的服务员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I didn't even know her. She was a cloakroom attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在帮她找我的票\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was helping her look for my ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那边有三件一模一样的粗呢大衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There were three duffle coats all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么那个衣架突然倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Somehow the rack collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都被压在下面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We were under all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在到处沾花惹草吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Were you playing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他干什么关你什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's it got to do with you what he gets up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底干了什么 -你自己知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What does he get up to? - You'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我会蠢到这种地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Because I'm that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,带自己的情人来见老婆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I play around and I bring her to meet the missus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个蠢婆娘 -你就是那么蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You silly cow. - But you are that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们能回家再说吗 暂时别吵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can we keep this stuff for back home, just for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,回家跟你那堆垃圾一起吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What, with the rest of the rubbish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你把廉价清洁剂 开胃水和贝塔录像机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You bring home cut-price detergents, tonic water,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都搬回了家 结果没一个卖得出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Betamax tapes and none of it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我都快被你的垃圾淹没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm drowning in your rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么和你说的 是不是说他是个大商人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What did he tell you? Did he say he's this big businessman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他才不是 他是个失败者 天生的失败者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}'Cause he's not. He's a failure. Born failure, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯需要一个好爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose needs a proper father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪 我在赚钱养活我们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie, I'm making a living. It keeps us fed, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不是这样的 你们爱着对方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're not like this. You love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 你不是不喜欢别人神经质兮兮的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pete, you never used to like them mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 说不定你还真喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Or I don't know, maybe you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你不小心… -杰琪 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If you're not careful... -- Jackie, wait, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别人结婚之日就是你离婚之日\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}there'll be a wedding and a divorce on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 让我和我太太好好谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Wait here. Give us a couple of minutes with the missus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧 把车挨着街角停好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Tell you what, straighten the car up. Stick it round the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别再惹什么乱子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't cause any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hey, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不听 肯定又是上次衣帽间事件重演\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm not listening. It's the duffle coats all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪 有时候毛呢大衣真的只是毛呢大衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie, sometimes a duffle coat is just a duffle coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的 我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Things will get better soon. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够你那些不靠谱的雄心壮志了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've had enough of all your daft schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃了上顿都不知道有没有下顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I never know where the next meal's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会搞定的 亲爱的 很快的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll get it right, love. One day soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证我会让我们好起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I promise you I'll get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怪兽 怪兽要吃我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Monsters! Going to eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么怪兽 亲爱的 是外星人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What sort of monsters, sweetheart? Is it aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,到教堂里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get in the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到教堂里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get in the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God. What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,萨拉 -待着别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sarah! - Stay in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,都进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}In!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们进不来 这种老式的门窗没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They can't get in. Old windows and doors. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,越古老越坚固\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The older something is, the stronger it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看别的门 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Go and check the other doors. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 它们是什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's happening? What are they? What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,时间出问题了 出现了伤痕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's been an accident in time. A wound in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它们就像是趁虚而入的病菌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They're like bacteria, taking advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时间 你在胡说些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What do you mean? Time? What are you jabbering on about time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该想到你会跟我吵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I might've known you'd argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪我受够你了 -你怎么知道我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie, I'm sick of you complaining. - How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我没空跟你扯了 -我这辈子从没见过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't have time for this! - I've never met you in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我不解决这事 你还真见不到我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, and you never will unless I sort this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话 我已经忍了很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now if you don't mind, I've waited a long time to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪·泰勒 照我说的做 去检查那些门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie Tyler, do as I say. Go and check the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就该这么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I should've done that ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸在外面 -你可以迟点再哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My dad was out there. - You can mourn him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在得集中注意力 让我们一起活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now we've got to concentrate on keeping ourselves alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸… -我也无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My dad had... - There is nothing I can do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不 但是他有这个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, but he had this phone thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法修好 但是一直有这个声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't get it to work. I keep getting this voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,华生 过来 我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Watson, come here. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世界上第一通电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's the very first phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历山大·格拉汉姆·贝尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Alexander Graham Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得电话应该没什么用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't think the telephone's gonna be much use.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总得报警\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Someone must have called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在警察帮不了你 没人能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The police can't help you now, no one can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙中没人能伤到它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nothing in this universe can harm those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,时间出现了裂口 它们是来给伤口消毒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Time's been damaged and they've come to sterilise the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,它们要抹杀所有的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}By consuming everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是因为…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is this because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的错吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is this my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,城里一些地方在冒烟 但是没有火警\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's smoke coming up from the city. But no sirens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不只是我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't think it's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这些东西到处都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think these things are all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可能全世界都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一辆车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Was that a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这不重要 不要担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not important. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的那个伙伴 什么叫这是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This mate of yours. What did he mean, this is your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 这一切吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't know. Just everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我的车钥匙给了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I gave you my car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我一般不会把钥匙给陌生人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't give your keys to a complete stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好像我很信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's like I trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我见到你那一刻就信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The moment I met you, I just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,时间的伤痕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A wound in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You called me Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你有我的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有杰琪的态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie's attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你大喊的时候就像她一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You sound like her when you shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是 你是 你是我的洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You are. You are. You're my Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我长大后的洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're my Rose, grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.28,0:24:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我的爸爸 我的爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Dad! My dad. My daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,您是… -博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mister? - Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像知道发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You seem to know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,的确如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I give that impression, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想问… -你能救我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I just wanted to ask... - Can you save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.33,0:24:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who are you two, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.86,0:24:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,斯图尔特·霍斯金斯 -萨拉·克拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stuart Hoskins. - Sarah Clark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.35,0:24:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个呢 男孩还是女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And one extra? Boy or girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.11,0:24:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我也不想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know. I don't want to know, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.07,0:24:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切是怎么开始的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How did all this get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.13,0:24:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,动感酒吧外 凌晨两点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Outside the Beatbox Club, 2:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.36,0:24:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,街角 我钱包丢了 没钱打车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Street corner, I'd lost my purse, didn't have money for a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.94,0:24:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我把她带回了家 -然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I took her home. - Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.06,0:24:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让她跟你去约会吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Asked her for a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.84,0:25:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把号码写在我手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Wrote his number on the back of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.80,0:25:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再也甩不掉她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Never got rid of her since.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.67,0:25:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My dad said...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.46,0:25:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know what this is all about
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们无足轻重…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and I know we're not important...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.71,0:25:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说你们无足轻重\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who said you're not important?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.10,0:25:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我去过各种各样的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've travelled to all sorts of places,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.80,0:25:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,干过很多你们无法想象的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}done things you couldn't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.32,0:25:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.96,0:25:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凌晨两点在街角打的回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Street corner, 2:00 in the morning, getting a taxi home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.44,0:25:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没经历过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've never had a life like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.68,0:25:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.32,0:25:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽力救你们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll try and save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.70,0:25:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.96,0:25:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我已经是爸爸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean, I'm already a dad
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.10,0:25:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是洛斯长大后变成你这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but Rose grows up and she's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.22,0:25:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.41,0:25:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说我还以为你不会有这么厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean, I suppose I thought that you'd be a bit useless
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.23,0:25:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有我的废物基因什么的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}what with my useless genes and all but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.42,0:26:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么来这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, I mean, how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.67,0:26:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想知道吗 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you really want to know? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.39,0:26:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,时光机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.63,0:26:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,时光机 -我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Time machine? - Cross my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.52,0:26:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个时候大家都有时光机了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you all have time machines where you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.36,0:26:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 只有博士有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, just the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.34,0:26:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道会出现这些东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did you know these things were coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.33,0:26:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.01,0:26:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 我不知道 我脑子里一片浆糊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}God, I don't know, my head's spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.53,0:26:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,未来是怎么样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's the future like?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.88,0:26:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.71,0:26:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么样 头发白了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What am I like? Have I gone grey?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.84,0:26:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我秃了吗 别告诉我我秃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Have I gone bald? Don't tell me I've gone bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这家伙不是你的男朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So, if this mate of yours isn't your boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.09,0:26:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说我还是很欣慰的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and I have to say I'm glad
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.54,0:26:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为作为你的父亲 我觉得他有点太老了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}'cause being your dad and all, I think he's a bit old for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.38,0:26:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你有男朋友吗 -没有 曾经有过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Have you got a bloke? - No. I did have.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.70,0:26:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.24,0:27:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.36,0:27:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着西服我还真认不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I just didn't recognise him in a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.99,0:27:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你得放开我 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You have to let go of me, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.61,0:27:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm always saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.67,0:27:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子看到什么就跟宝贝一样抱住\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He just grabs hold of what's passing and holds on for dear life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.19,0:27:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他以后有女朋友了 那姑娘还真可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}God help his poor girlfriend if he ever gets one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.75,0:27:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我和洛斯只是在聊天 -聊天是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Me and Rose were just talking. - Oh, yeah? Talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.80,0:27:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当世界要毁灭时 你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}While the world comes to an end, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.26,0:27:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,黏着某个年轻的金发妞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Cling to the youngest blonde.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.32,0:27:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 米奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on, Mick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.09,0:27:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能告诉她 -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You can't tell her. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.31,0:27:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说我不希望你告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean, I really don't want you to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.69,0:27:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不希望让别人知道吗 -我那个时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't want people to know? - Where I come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.23,0:27:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪连播放器的时间条都搞不定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie doesn't know how to work the timer on the video recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.05,0:27:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我上礼拜才教过她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I showed her that last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.83,0:27:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Point taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.41,0:27:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 你才不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose, you're not going to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.75,0:27:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让世界毁灭的 对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}bring about the end of the world, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.11,0:27:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.71,0:28:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪让我照顾她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie gave her to me to look after.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.83,0:28:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真是时过境迁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How times change.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.02,0:28:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是小心点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚给米奇留下了鸡妈妈一样的印象\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think I just imprinted myself on Mickey like a mother chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.70,0:28:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别碰宝宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No. Don't touch the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.54,0:28:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是同一个人 这是悖论\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're both the same person, that's a paradox.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.35,0:28:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不希望发生悖论 外面还有这些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We don't want a paradox happening, not with these things outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.83,0:28:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,时间的任何扰动都会增强它们的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Anything new, any disturbance in time, makes them stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.09,0:28:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,悖论甚至可能把它们放进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A paradox might let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.99,0:28:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都做不对 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't do anything right, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.96,0:28:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你都这么问了 没错 所以别碰宝宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Since you asked, no. So, don't touch the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.09,0:28:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不笨 -你别想骗我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm not stupid. - You could have fooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.09,0:28:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.90,0:28:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.25,0:28:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我没打算真的扔下你一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wasn't really gonna leave you on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.89,0:28:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.16,0:28:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,实话告诉你 我毫无头绪 完全没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Between you and me, I haven't got a plan. No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.82,0:29:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.90,0:29:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你会想出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.29,0:29:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,整个地球都受到了侵蚀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The entire Earth's been sterilised.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.97,0:29:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 还有其他地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This, and other places like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.49,0:29:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,全人类就只剩下这几个人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}are all that's left of the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.55,0:29:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能还能撑一会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We might hold out for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.71,0:29:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是根本挡不住这些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but nothing can stop those creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.43,0:29:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它们还是会闯进来 这些墙不够古老\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They'll get through in the end. The walls aren't that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.97,0:29:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没法阻止它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And there's nothing I can do to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.28,0:29:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,本来有阻止这类事态的法则\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There used to be laws stopping this kind of thing from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.75,0:29:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的族人本来能阻止这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My people would have stopped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.45,0:29:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们都不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But they're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.32,0:29:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我也要随他们而去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And now I'm going the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.70,0:29:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我知道…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If I'd realised...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.47,0:29:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.79,0:29:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}tell me you're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.51,0:29:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.31,0:29:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.41,0:30:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么有东西在发热\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Have you got something hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.83,0:30:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是塔迪斯的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's the TARDIS key.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.57,0:30:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这说明钥匙还跟塔迪斯连着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's telling me it's still connected to the TARDIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.96,0:30:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的飞船的内部被甩到了时间伤痕之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The inside of my ship was thrown out of the wound
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.12,0:30:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们能用这个找回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but we can use this to bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.29,0:30:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我把飞船找回来 就能修复好一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And once I've got my ship back, then I can mend everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.13,0:30:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只需要一点电 你们谁有电池吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, I just need a bit of power. Has anybody got a battery?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.31,0:30:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个够大了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This one big enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.34,0:30:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妙极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.17,0:30:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好老爹 拿着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good old Dad. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.67,0:30:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要稍微充个电\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just need to do a bit of charging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.35,0:30:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就能把大家带回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And then we can bring everyone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.77,0:31:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没说你为什么要来这里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You, erm, you never said why you came here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.08,0:31:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我有个时光机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If I had a time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.09,0:31:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会觉得1987年有什么特别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wouldn't have thought 1987 was anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.93,0:31:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,至少这附近没啥特别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not round here, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.19,0:31:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是碰巧 -我真幸运啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We just ended up here. - Lucky for me, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.99,0:31:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你没有救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If you hadn't been there to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.28,0:31:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是个巧合\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.77,0:31:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那真的只是运气好 太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That was just really good luck. It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.83,0:31:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那在未来 我和她还生活在一起吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So, in the future, are me and her indoors still together?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.25,0:31:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你还和我们住在一起吗 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You still living with us? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.89,0:31:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个好爸爸吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Am I a good dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.60,0:31:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.75,0:32:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候你每天都会给我讲睡前故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You told me a bedtime story every night when I was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.26,0:32:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你每晚都会来 从来不会错过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You were always there, you never missed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.35,0:32:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.80,0:32:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你每周六都会带我们去乡间野餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}you took us for picnics in the country every Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.31,0:32:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你从来不会让我们失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You never let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.80,0:32:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直陪伴着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You were there for us all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.58,0:32:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个值得依赖的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Someone I could really rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.82,0:32:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.57,0:33:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 所有人都不准碰那把钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right, no one touches that key,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.06,0:33:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听懂了没 不准碰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}have you got that? Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.76,0:33:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有人碰 就会啪的一下消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Anyone touches that key, it'll be, well, zap!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.66,0:33:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要碰它 一切都会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just leave it be and everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.36,0:33:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大家都会逃出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We'll get out. All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.45,0:33:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,斯图尔特 萨拉 你俩能结婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stuart, Sarah, you're gonna get married, just like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.04,0:33:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当时间回到原样…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}When time gets sorted out...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.31,0:33:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都会忘记发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Everybody here forgets what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.62,0:33:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 你改变的事情还是会保持下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And don't worry, the thing that you changed will stay changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.00,0:33:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我会活下去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You mean I'll still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.00,0:33:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我应该死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Though I'm meant to be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.54,0:34:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我这一生中什么都没干\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's why I haven't done anything with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.85,0:34:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这一生毫无意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why it didn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.24,0:34:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样的 -扯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doesn't work like that. - Rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.04,0:34:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我太没用了 死都死不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was so useless I couldn't even die properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.73,0:34:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在发生这一切都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now it's my fault all this has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.22,0:34:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的错 -不 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is my fault. - No, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.99,0:34:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.78,0:34:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的错 我的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's my job for it to be my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.06,0:34:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她的父亲 你怎么会是她的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Her dad? How are you her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.45,0:34:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你几岁生的她 十二岁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How old were you? 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.98,0:34:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太恶心了 -杰琪 听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, that's disgusting. - Jacks, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.91,0:34:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是洛斯 -洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is Rose. - Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.93,0:34:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太变态了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How sick is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.58,0:34:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然给咱们的女儿起了个二手名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did you give my daughter a second-hand name?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.66,0:34:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,到底有几个 你都叫他们洛斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How many are there? Do you call them all Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.22,0:34:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的分上 这就是洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, for God's sake, look. It's the same Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.45,0:34:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 不 \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.64,0:34:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都躲到我后面来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Everyone, behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.38,0:35:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这里最老的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm the oldest thing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.43,0:35:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.90,0:35:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,冷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.03,0:35:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙是冷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The key's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.43,0:35:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.43,0:36:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩 你们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Both of you, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.49,0:36:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.48,0:36:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样了 我们完了 结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is it. There's nothing we can do. It's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.49,0:37:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,博士真的很在乎你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Doctor really cared about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.05,0:37:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想让你再经历一次伤痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He didn't want you to go through it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.77,0:37:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,总想尝试另外的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not if there was another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.05,0:37:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在别无选择了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.42,0:37:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.16,0:37:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那辆本应杀死我的车 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The car that should have killed me, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.54,0:37:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.42,0:37:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,博士早就发现了 但是他…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Doctor worked it out way back but he...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.45,0:37:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他想保护我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}tried to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.41,0:38:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Still.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.24,0:38:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在已经不是他说了算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's not in charge anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.10,0:38:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.73,0:38:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这样 -我是谁 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But you can't. - Who am I, love?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.61,0:38:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.70,0:38:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,杰琪 看看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackie, look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.59,0:38:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我们的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.46,0:38:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.39,0:38:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我注定要死 杰琪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm meant to be dead, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.36,0:38:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于要摆脱我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're gonna get rid of me at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.05,0:38:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.89,0:38:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这辈子就信我这一次 必须要这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}For once in your life, trust me. It's got to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.53,0:38:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你得活下去 因为你得养大我们的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've got to survive 'cause you've got to bring up our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.55,0:39:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没给你讲过睡前故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I never read you those bedtime stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.83,0:39:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也从来没带你去过野餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I never took you on those picnics.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.32,0:39:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有陪过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was never there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.92,0:39:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你本应跟我们一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You would've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.70,0:39:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可以为你做这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But I can do this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.65,0:39:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在可以做你的好爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can be a proper dad to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.73,0:39:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我还多活了这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've had all these extra hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.91,0:39:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上没人有过这种待遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No one else in the world has ever had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.51,0:39:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外 我还见到了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And on top of that, I get to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.02,0:39:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And you're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.99,0:39:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我是多么幸运啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How lucky am I, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.57,0:39:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 乖乖听爸爸的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So, come on. Do as your dad says.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.93,0:39:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你会陪着我吗 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You gonna be there for me, love?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.00,0:40:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.33,0:40:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Goodbye, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.07,0:41:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看他吧 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Go to him. Quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.98,0:41:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那司机只是个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The driver was just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.31,0:42:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他停下来等着警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He stopped, he waited for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.03,0:42:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It wasn't his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.46,0:42:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么 彼得突然冲出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}For some reason, Pete just ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.78,0:42:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,人们说有个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}People say there was this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.89,0:42:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得死前她陪在他的身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And she sat with Pete while he was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.56,0:42:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她牵着他的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She held his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.41,0:42:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.75,0:42:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谁也不知道她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Never found out who she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.79,0:42:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得·艾伦·泰勒 我爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Peter Alan Tyler, my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.66,0:42:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界上最棒的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The most wonderful man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.68,0:43:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,死于1987年11月7日\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Died 7th November, 1987.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.74,0:43:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\an8\fad(500,400)\pos(171.856,183.273)}{\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.41,0:43:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们追它做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And why are we chasing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.51,0:43:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是它淡紫色级别的危险啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's mauve and dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.81,0:43:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且再过30秒就要撞到伦敦市中心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and about 30 seconds from the centre of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.43,0:43:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.46,0:43:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,求你放我进来 妈咪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Please let me in, Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.50,0:43:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他碰到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You mustn't let him touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.52,0:43:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是医生吗 -当过一阵子 \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are you a doctor? - I have my moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.09,0:43:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的伤势完全相同\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They've all got the same injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.44,0:43:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,连手背上的伤疤都一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right down to the scar on the back of the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.71,0:43:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,虽是皮肉伤 却如瘟疫般传播\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Physical injuries as plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.22,0:43:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hello. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.64,0:43:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,到阳台上喝一杯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Shall we have a drink on the balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.71,0:43:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得自己更像个罪犯 -我也这么觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I like to think of myself as a criminal. - I bet you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
